{"tid":115001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"猥褻拍攝170童裸照　日警逮6人含2教師","createTime":"2017-02-10T08:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T12:51:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88a33f5b4ec35fc2f8a0aa41336a42fa5c7f4bb0","tid":115001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">2017/02/09 21:02 3569</span><br />\n<br />\n日本一群戀童癖大叔與青年拍攝4歲至13歲男童裸照或影片，又以塗藥為由撫摸他們，警方一共逮捕6人。35歲嫌犯開發哲也2015年開始以自然體驗教室為名，招攬兒童參加，當年8歲的受害者表示，他睡著後衣服被脫下，下半身被觸摸，同時還被拍照攝影。另外，有受傷男童在睡覺時，嫌犯以幫忙擦藥為由，一邊撫摸他們的身體一邊拍照。嫌犯犯案地點從群馬縣、熊本縣到千葉縣露營場都有，他還帶其他3名網路上認識的大學生一起拍照猥褻兒童，又把拍下的幼童照片散布給另外兩名男子，一人是代課老師，另一人是退休老師。警方在他們的電腦發現超過10萬則影片或照片，受害者將近170人。（余浚安／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170209/640_3e9bc585dc9431cd01aedacf916ef914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170209%2F640_3e9bc585dc9431cd01aedacf916ef914.jpg&h=643c3b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170209/1052739/EDITOR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170209%2F1052739%2FEDITOR&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNWwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=98e0033d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170209/1052739/EDITOR</a>"},{"pid":"459a2c1ffde3bab23ddb12c0422791df0ddf6811","tid":115001,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"6人含2教師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開發哲也 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n孌童犯必須死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b925933f8505f5597e194cd4031a28eea7b436b","tid":115001,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"男童都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f864e1d2729c73878382eb5ea40a912e300985","tid":115001,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6人含2教師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開發哲也 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n孌童犯必須死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6個含2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e04c1b6f4b3934776d61bba4c4842b2c5a963a","tid":115001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}